      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "My Muse the Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Wife of a Reckless Artist",
        "Description": "My husband is one of those artsy-\r\nfartsy types, you know the kind.\r\nSees a sunset...cries. Well, he\r\nheard Mizutsune are \u0022creatures\r\nthat inspire creativity\u0022 so he ran\r\noff with his easel to find one. *sigh*\r\nCan you go save him for me?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Ma muse, le Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Femme d\u0027artiste t\u00E9m\u00E9raire",
        "Description": "Mon mari a une \u0022\u00E2me d\u0027artiste\u0022, tu\r\nsais. En gros, il pleure devant la\r\nbeaut\u00E9 d\u0027un coucher de soleil...\r\nBref, il para\u00EEt que le Mizutsune\r\n\u0022aiderait \u00E0 la cr\u00E9ativit\u00E9\u0022, donc mon\r\nmari est parti en chercher un avec\r\nson chevalet... Sauve-le pour moi.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il Mizutsune, la mia musa",
        "Client": "Moglie del pittore incauto",
        "Description": "Mio marito \u00E8 quel genere di\r\nartista che scoppia a piangere\r\ndavanti a un tramonto. Ora ha\r\nsentito che i Mizutsune\r\n\u0022stimolano la creativit\u00E0\u0022,\r\nquindi \u00E8 corso via per\r\ntrovarne uno. Puoi salvarlo?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Meine Muse, der Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Frau des tollk\u00FChnen Malers",
        "Description": "Mein Mann ist ein typischer Pseudo-\r\nk\u00FCnstler. Du wei\u00DFt schon, sieht einen\r\nSonnenuntergang und weint. Tja, er\r\nhat geh\u00F6rt, Mizutsune w\u00FCrden Krea-\r\ntivit\u00E4t inspirieren und ist mit seiner\r\nStaffelei losgelaufen, um einen zu\r\nfinden. *seufz* Rettest du ihn bitte?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Mizutsune.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Embelesado por un Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Mujer de un artista osado",
        "Description": "Mi marido es de esos artistas\r\nque lloran con una puesta de\r\nsol. Le han dicho que los\r\nMizutsune son criaturas\r\ninspiradoras y se ha ido a\r\npintarlos... Ains... \u00BFPodr\u00EDas\r\nir a salvarlo?",
        "Target": "Caza un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041C\u043E\u044F \u043C\u0443\u0437\u0430-\u041C\u0438\u0434\u0437\u0443\u0446\u0443\u043D\u044D",
        "Client": "\u0416\u0435\u043D\u0430 \u0431\u0435\u0441\u043F\u0435\u0447\u043D\u043E\u0433\u043E \u0445\u0443\u0434\u043E\u0436\u043D\u0438\u043A\u0430",
        "Description": "\u041C\u043E\u0439 \u043C\u0443\u0436 \u2014 \u0445\u0443\u0434\u043E\u0436\u043D\u0438\u043A, \u0443\u0442\u043E\u043D\u0447\u0435\u043D\u043D\u0430\u044F\r\n\u043D\u0430\u0442\u0443\u0440\u0430. \u0417\u0430\u043A\u0430\u0442 \u0443\u0432\u0438\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u2014 \u043F\u043B\u0430\u0447\u0435\u0442.\r\n\u041E\u043D \u0443\u0441\u043B\u044B\u0448\u0430\u043B \u0433\u0434\u0435-\u0442\u043E, \u0447\u0442\u043E\r\n\u041C\u0438\u0434\u0437\u0443\u0446\u0443\u043D\u044D \u0432\u0434\u043E\u0445\u043D\u043E\u0432\u043B\u044F\u044E\u0442 \u043D\u0430\r\n\u0442\u0432\u043E\u0440\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043E \u0438 \u043C\u0438\u0433\u043E\u043C \u0443\u0431\u0435\u0436\u0430\u043B \u0438\u0445\r\n\u0438\u0441\u043A\u0430\u0442\u044C. *\u0432\u0437\u0434\u044B\u0445\u0430\u0435\u0442* \u041C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0442,\r\n\u0441\u043F\u0430\u0441\u0435\u0448\u044C \u043C\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043D\u044C\u043A\u0430 \u043C\u043E\u0435\u0433\u043E?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041C\u0438\u0434\u0437\u0443\u0446\u0443\u043D\u044D",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
